# 9. Benefits of Claude Code

Using Claude Code offers several practical advantages.

* Reduces repetitive manual work.
* Understands large projects more effectively than isolated code snippets.
* Helps developers onboard unfamiliar codebases.
* Validates changes through testing.
* Encourages iterative development.
* Improves productivity for both individual developers and teams.

