```

Only after understanding the relationships does Claude generate an explanation.

---

## Why Context Matters

Imagine reading only one page of a novel.

You wouldn't understand the story.

Similarly, reading a single source file rarely explains an entire feature.

Claude gathers context before making decisions.

---

