# 1. Introduction

After installing Claude Code, the next step is learning how to interact with it effectively.

Unlike ChatGPT, Claude Code isn't designed for casual conversation. It is designed to work **inside your software project**.

When you start Claude Code, you're essentially inviting an AI software engineer into your project.

That engineer can:

* Read your source code
* Understand your project
* Execute commands
* Modify files
* Run tests
* Explain architecture

The quality of Claude's work depends largely on **how you start your session** and **how you communicate your goals**.

