## What Happens Behind the Scenes?

When Claude starts:

* Detects current directory
* Loads project
* Loads CLAUDE.md (if available)
* Loads project configuration
* Loads available tools
* Waits for your prompt

Nothing is modified until you ask Claude to perform an action.

