# 11. Using Context Effectively

Context helps Claude make informed decisions.

Instead of:

```text
Fix the bug.
```

Provide background.

```text
Users started receiving HTTP 500 errors after yesterday's deployment.

The issue only occurs for premium users.

Investigate the backend service responsible for subscription validation.
```

This saves Claude from unnecessary exploration.

