↓

Read 20 Files

↓

Run Tests

↓

Fix Errors

↓

Run Build

↓

Read Logs

↓

Read Documentation

↓

Generate Code
```

Each step increases the amount of stored information.

Eventually:

```text
Context

███████████████░░░░
```

Claude is approaching its limit.

